00:19:21.720 --> 00:19:24.800
O našoj noći na koncertu.

00:19:30.040 --> 00:19:31.240
Izvini me.

00:19:31.960 --> 00:19:33.320
Gori!

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:36.720
Gori!
Gori! Gori!

00:19:41.000 --> 00:19:43.000
Gori! Gori!

